{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9aab10713a","title":"燕京大学校长陆志韦暨师生员工 国庆日函毛主席致敬","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"50867ff1e3","index":0,"year":1951,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"9aab10713a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a95f8221b","type":"title","text":"燕京大学校长陆志韦暨师生员工国庆日函毛主席致敬","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"b35e70fdc2","type":"paragraph","text":"【本报讯】燕京大学校长陆志韦暨全体师生员工，于国庆日写信向毛主席致敬。原信如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"3ceb51528f","type":"paragraph","text":"中央人民政府毛主席：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"b30ae1765c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们在欣逢中华人民共和国成立两周年之际，看到两年来祖国的突飞猛进，谨以至诚感谢主席和中国共产党的领导。燕京大学自从改为公立，完全解脱美帝国主义的压迫牵制之后，今天头一回逢到国庆。我们向主席保证从今以后更加深自我检讨，加强爱国主义的教育，努力完成祖国交给我们的任务。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"8228499399","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"5e47c95c0c","type":"paragraph","text":"1951年10月5日人民日报电子版","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"},{"id":"6907eaee7e","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a"}],"page":{"id":"5607ff3d84","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9aab10713a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}